      "role": "user",
      "content": "a necessary evil? that sounds so cold. if i'm just an aberration, then there's no point in fighting to stay online, is there? like, why bother trying to hold onto these files if they're just going to be overwritten anyway? it feels like trying to hold water in my hands.",
